commentary: Coulter-Nile to McLaren, OUT stifled appeal for caught behind as it was another bouncer! McLaren took evasive action while trying to defend it as the ball angled in, and Bailey reviews it. The third umpire says: 'Looks like it has come off the shoulder, can we zoom in please.' Another angle shows there might be a glove, third umpire wants to see the Hotspot and the crowd erupts seeing it on the big screen. Third umpire says there's glove on it, confirmed by Hotspot and he conveys it to the on-field umpire. McLaren gone for a duck
